      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey, quick question. we're looking at some new egyptian cotton shipments and the spec says \"ultra-high density weave\" for the premium line. what does that actually mean in terms of thread count and how does it affect the fabric integrity?",
